title: Is dark star Singularity supposed to be up?

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body:
Just wondering if the times are right?

It says up from 4:00am Australian time on the 5th of may. Which was this morning.
But its not up?

replies.body: I'm unable to actually select the game mode, as it says "category not currently available". Is this because I don't have Dark Star Thresh, that sounds a bit stupid, but I was just unsure and I'm looking for clarification.
There shouldn't be anything blocking you.  Have you tried restarting the client?
An update just needed to be applied, thank you for the suggestion.

Looks like the website has incorrect information here around the enable times for Dark Star. This should be enabled between 11am and 3am - up until 3am on the 16th. We're working to get the site updated with the correct information now.
They seem pretty slow getting game-modes up
